categories: Category:Missions of the Galactic Civil War

nodes.text: In around 1 ABY, a mission was carried out by Renegade Squadron on the planet Naboo. The Renegades assaulted an Imperial weapons depot and found data concerning the new superweapon, the Star Destroyer Conqueror. They later attacked the research facility where the superlaser for the Conqueror had been developed and learned more about the Star Destroyer.
